reviewText: Out of all the items I purchased this item was the worst one, I couldn't watch it on a regular dvd nor on my ps3. If I could return it i would,  but i won't because it would cost more to return it than what i paid., plus I went to target and purchased it for $10.
Condition exactly as described.  Item is great.  Good shipping & price.  Good version of T1 on DVD, extras are really good, double sided.
